{"tid":699871,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【賤男呃女全直擊】諗盡方法呃買手機 記者踢爆即當街狂奔","createTime":"2018-06-13T01:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T15:18:12.000Z","uid":125279,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"5bdb5625ff1e24072a38d372ee374f452f264521","tid":699871,"uid":125279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:24:27.000Z","msg":"一名港女苦主，上月被氹送厚禮，人渣食過翻尋味，又再出動......... <br />\n<br />\n苦主Helen在上月透過交友app認識柏圖，經過一段時間的短訊溝通，柏圖終於出擊邀約Helen見面，再以同一個劇本，生日送禮物環節，成功氹到Helen送上2000元現金，「佢話要揾相熟朋友做西裝，打比朋友時仲話係未來女朋友送。」奸計得逞，渣男柏圖甚至提出更大膽要求，要求生日飯折現，結果Helen再次乖乖奉上500大元，最後換來柏圖請她吃了一頓餃子晚飯。 <br />\n<br />\n本周日，柏圖食過翻尋味，提出約會，Helen配合記者放蛇，再約對方見面。   甫見面，柏圖即送上手鏈，透露此乃母親意思，及後着Helen回禮，目標希望能送贈Apple產品予愛好打機的父母。 <br />\n<br />\n記者上前踢爆，問柏圖為何經常以生日為由氹人送禮，柏圖聞言即拔足狂奔，落荒而逃。 <br />\n<br />\n撰文：艾馬 <br />\n<br />\n攝影：王晴 <br />\n<br />\n<ins><a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180613/2_593495_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180613%2F2_593495_0&d=jLxFJ%2FU7YEb3387IAD0s03Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e34bf076\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180613%2F2_593495_0&h=26f2523c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180613/2_593495_0</a></ins>"},{"pid":"8de98fa5cbea77795562587fe3308b2ae1eca0c1","tid":699871,"uid":125279,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:29:47.000Z","msg":"有無人知佢係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蘋果記者連格仔都唔打，佢實比fd笑到臉都黃，呃肥婆錢"},{"pid":"daed27f74ec159e05afb7d889e299cb941377ba1","tid":699871,"uid":108467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8de98fa5cbea77795562587fe3308b2ae1eca0c1","tid":699871,"uid":125279,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:29:47.000Z","msg":"有無人知佢係邊個<img src=\"/assets/fac